1. *Uzimam* malo vremena da se odmorim. (I'm taking a little time to rest.)
2. *Uzimala* je njegovu ruku u svoju. (She took his hand in hers.)
3. *Uzme* li on izlazak u kazino? (Will he take an outing to the casino?)
4. *Uzimamo* lekcije iz istorije. (We are taking lessons in history.)
5. *Uzeo* je novčanik i otišao. (He took his wallet and left.)